        <Summary>A Lightweight Panel and Taskbar</Summary>
        <Description>Tint2 is a simple panel and taskbar intentionally made for openbox3, but should also work with other window managers. The goal is to keep a clean and unintrusive look with code lightweight and compliance with freedesktop specifications.</Description>
